rpentry</strong> improves your idle experience - automate gameplay & gain growing bonuses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980530/extras/271fa9d7a72f63c549c5ea6ff0d3901f.avif?t=1772539262\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Prestige to unlock features, bonuses & tons of sweet multipliers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize your progression, grow your Koins higher, sacrifice more and more and more kings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Transcend further beyond - the demonikiwi cycle never ends.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980530/extras/6dbcb7919816f4e437b73d7c4dd1bc02.poster.avif?t=1772539262\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980530/extras/6dbcb7919816f4e437b73d7c4dd1bc02.webm?t=1772539262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980530/extras/6dbcb7919816f4e437b73d7c4dd1bc02.mp4?t=1772539262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
